tom-rte"><div class=3D"custom-rte"><p>The evolution of this reporting requi=
rement serves as a clear signal to the digital asset owner and user that th=
e US government is keenly aware of and is monitoring the evolutionary natur=
e of crypto=E2=80=94and that it intends to continue to do so.</p>
<p>So, what do you need to know right now? To help ensure proper tax report=
ing and avoid any tax controversy related to your digital assets, it=E2=80=
=99s critical that you take a hard look at seven key types of transactions.=
</p>
</div>
</div>
