 <p>The evolution of this reporting requirement serves as a clear signal to=
 the digital asset owner and user that the US government is keenly aware of=
 and is monitoring the evolutionary nature of crypto=E2=80=94and that it in=
tends to continue to do so.</p>
 <p>So, what do you need to know right now? To help ensure proper tax repor=
ting and avoid any tax controversy related to your digital assets, it=E2=80=
=99s critical that you take a hard look at seven key types of transactions.=
</p><!--language div end-->
</div></div></div>
