 <p>What does all this mean? In short, more new forms, new types of transac=
tions and new types of reporting to the IRS, all of which, in turn, may tra=
nslate to more potential audits. To get this right, it=E2=80=99s best to ha=
ve a trusted adviser to guide you through this thicket of often unclear and=
 uncertain regulation.</p><!--language div end-->
